title: Loafer
subTitle: Seenu, a man who wants to go to Dubai, meets and falls in love with Madhumati. When he discovers that a dreaded don has killed his friend and Madhumati's brother, he sets out to exact revenge.

title: Sivudu
subTitle: A carefree young man's life is disrupted by rising crime in his locality and when his family faces danger, he decides to fight back.

title: Bal Ganesh And The Friends From Zeba
subTitle: Three ardent followers of Bal Ganesh share the admired deity's incredible stories with their guests from the planet Zeba.

title: Veeram
subTitle: Two brothers, raised by their sister, take opposite path, one honest, the other criminal. When tragedy strikes and the criminal brother dies, the honest one seeks vengeance.

title: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
subTitle: Kannabiran, a lawyer, saves a young woman from a pornography racket run by Inba, a minister's son. However, Inba threatens to leak explicit videos of several women, making Kannabiran go after him.

title: Kali Kitaab
subTitle: When narratives from a cryptic book spring to life, a woman experiences bizarre phenomena and resolves to uncover the identity of its enigmatic writer.

title: Asli Fighter
subTitle: To free their imprisoned boss, a group of terrorists plan to bomb a flyover in Hyderabad. Amid all the chaos, unfortunately, a man and a woman get entangled in their plan.

title: Double Attack
subTitle: Siddharth and Charan, two lookalikes who are fighting their own battles against evildoers, cross paths and join forces to take down Rawat, a ruthless minister.

title: Secret Agent

title: Meri Ladaai
subTitle: An ambitious real estate agent falls in love with the sister of a powerful business tycoon. However, the girl's brother resents their relationship and tries to separate the lovers.

title: Super Ranga
subTitle: Ranga, a reckless thrill-seeker, falls in love with Swathi who makes him promise to be more responsible. However, she breaks up with him when he goes back to his old ways.

title: Dackalti

subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.

subTitle: Arya, a righteous man, falls in love with a small-town woman named Geetha, unaware of the obstacles that lie ahead for both of them.

subTitle: Nalan, a restauranteur with a complicated love life, unwillingly gets embroiled in a series of strange events after a miniature mummy sarcophagus ends up in his restaurant.

title: Friday The 13th
subTitle: The 13th page of a mysterious book harbours evil. It gives rise to a series of devastating events as people who read it, get possessed by demonic spirits.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Agent Chanakya

title: Pichaikkaran

title: Jaguar

title: The Warriorr
subTitle: Satya, a doctor, is brutally beaten and driven out of his city by Guru, a ruthless gangster. However, Satya returns two years later as a police officer to exact revenge on Guru.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.
